1
00:01:27,420 --> 00:01:31,920
[The Dark Romance]

2
00:01:32,160 --> 00:01:34,920
[Episode 16]

3
00:02:17,710 --> 00:02:18,240
Hello?

4
00:02:18,870 --> 00:02:20,730
I found it on the foreign network.

5
00:02:21,070 --> 00:02:23,310
Ms. Yan usually looks gentle and refined.

6
00:02:23,310 --> 00:02:25,840
I didn't expect her
to play so wild in private.

7
00:02:25,910 --> 00:02:26,800
Who is that man?

8
00:02:27,280 --> 00:02:28,470
Do you want to use this video

9
00:02:28,470 --> 00:02:29,630
to humiliate her relentlessly

10
00:02:29,630 --> 00:02:32,190
and make her unable to hold her head up
in front of you for the rest of her life?

11
00:02:32,190 --> 00:02:34,720
Is this low-level method
all you can think of?

12
00:02:36,579 --> 00:02:37,800
Use a safe alt account

13
00:02:38,590 --> 00:02:39,590
to post it.

14
00:02:42,530 --> 00:02:43,850
She is your wife.

15
00:02:44,150 --> 00:02:46,350
Aren't you afraid of a pyrrhic victory?

16
00:02:47,860 --> 00:02:49,329
How could she be my enemy?

17
00:02:52,000 --> 00:02:53,140
An enemy

18
00:02:53,360 --> 00:02:54,350
will defend

19
00:02:54,470 --> 00:02:55,150
and resist.

20
00:02:56,000 --> 00:02:56,750
What we need to do

21
00:02:56,750 --> 00:02:58,680
is not stand against her,

22
00:02:59,190 --> 00:03:00,310
but find a position

23
00:03:01,630 --> 00:03:04,080
where she'll always look up to you.

24
00:03:05,520 --> 00:03:06,710
When she looks up to you

25
00:03:06,710 --> 00:03:07,790
and needs you,

26
00:03:07,910 --> 00:03:10,520
that's how you own the whole relationship.

27
00:03:13,400 --> 00:03:15,330
When she questions your position,

28
00:03:15,710 --> 00:03:17,370
you shouldn't argue with her,

29
00:03:18,400 --> 00:03:20,030
but make her admit

30
00:03:22,310 --> 00:03:24,510
that she can only be in a lower position.

31
00:03:25,850 --> 00:03:28,530
Then she will willingly look up to you.

32
00:03:29,520 --> 00:03:30,400
So is this

33
00:03:30,400 --> 00:03:32,060
how you make her look up to you?

34
00:03:37,190 --> 00:03:38,920
That's all for today's lesson.

35
00:03:39,750 --> 00:03:41,360
I'm afraid you won't be able to digest it
if I say too much.

36
00:03:41,360 --> 00:03:42,360
Wait, wait, wait.

37
00:03:42,590 --> 00:03:43,960
I have one more question.

38
00:03:43,960 --> 00:03:45,520
Why is your tattoo Medusa?

39
00:03:46,190 --> 00:03:48,050
Doesn't everyone who sees Medusa

40
00:03:48,360 --> 00:03:49,310
turn to stone?

41
00:03:51,360 --> 00:03:53,980
But in the end,
her head was cut off by Perseus

42
00:03:55,390 --> 00:03:56,800
and became his medal.

43
00:04:23,800 --> 00:04:24,240
Hello?

44
00:04:24,960 --> 00:04:25,490
Yan Ling.

45
00:04:26,480 --> 00:04:28,210
Have you seen that post online?

46
00:04:28,360 --> 00:04:29,160
What post?

47
00:04:29,360 --> 00:04:31,220
I'll send it for you to take a look.

48
00:04:39,670 --> 00:04:40,150
[Huge plot twist!
I actually saw this on X.]

49
00:04:40,170 --> 00:04:40,570
[A steamy video of the female professor
messing around with her ex-husband.]

50
00:04:40,590 --> 00:04:41,140
[She's this wild
yet accuses others of assault?]

51
00:04:42,420 --> 00:04:43,480
[Maybe intellectuals]

52
00:04:43,510 --> 00:04:45,020
[just have unique ways to relieve stress.]

53
00:04:45,580 --> 00:04:46,230
[How can someone like her be a professor?]
[University professors sure live wild.]

54
00:04:52,720 --> 00:04:58,870
[Police]

55
00:05:00,750 --> 00:05:01,810
I'm sorry, Ms. Yan.

56
00:05:02,830 --> 00:05:03,670
Actually,

57
00:05:04,070 --> 00:05:05,600
when we caught Ouyang
and the others that day,

58
00:05:05,600 --> 00:05:07,720
we confiscated all the videos on the spot

59
00:05:07,720 --> 00:05:08,830
to prevent leakage.

60
00:05:08,830 --> 00:05:10,150
But I guess

61
00:05:10,240 --> 00:05:12,160
when they were playing it,

62
00:05:12,180 --> 00:05:14,510
it had been uploaded
to the foreign network.

63
00:05:14,510 --> 00:05:17,110
And the person
who posted this is very cunning.

64
00:05:17,600 --> 00:05:18,750
In the video he posted,

65
00:05:18,750 --> 00:05:20,510
both of your faces...

66
00:05:21,680 --> 00:05:23,940
and private parts are slightly blurred.

67
00:05:24,430 --> 00:05:25,160
So this behavior

68
00:05:25,160 --> 00:05:26,720
doesn't constitute a crime.

69
00:05:26,720 --> 00:05:28,630
At most, it's civil infringement.

70
00:05:28,630 --> 00:05:29,750
You have to claim

71
00:05:29,750 --> 00:05:30,720
infringement on your reputation

72
00:05:30,720 --> 00:05:32,720
and the right to privacy on your own.

73
00:05:33,270 --> 00:05:33,750
Wait.

74
00:05:34,159 --> 00:05:35,950
Those people are too irresponsible.

75
00:05:35,950 --> 00:05:37,120
That's just nonsense

76
00:05:37,120 --> 00:05:37,920
on there.

77
00:05:38,510 --> 00:05:40,310
Actually, it's really strange.

78
00:05:40,510 --> 00:05:42,950
I've read the records
given by my cybersecurity colleagues.

79
00:05:42,950 --> 00:05:44,190
Many of the accounts in the post

80
00:05:44,190 --> 00:05:45,840
that blindly slander you

81
00:05:46,000 --> 00:05:47,320
were just registered.

82
00:05:47,690 --> 00:05:49,500
They'll use the same content repeatedly

83
00:05:49,500 --> 00:05:51,620
for a while to gain more attention.

84
00:05:54,700 --> 00:05:55,900
What does that mean?

85
00:05:57,120 --> 00:05:57,630
Ms. Yan.

86
00:05:58,630 --> 00:05:59,730
Think carefully,

87
00:06:00,240 --> 00:06:01,240
have you recently

88
00:06:01,750 --> 00:06:02,800
offended anyone?

89
00:06:03,360 --> 00:06:04,820
And I feel like this person

90
00:06:05,040 --> 00:06:06,970
should be quite familiar with you.

91
00:06:14,270 --> 00:06:15,870
I did offend someone.

92
00:06:17,720 --> 00:06:18,950
But he deserved it.

93
00:06:19,720 --> 00:06:21,190
Forget it. Let him be.

94
00:06:29,430 --> 00:06:29,920
Right.

95
00:06:31,180 --> 00:06:33,300
Is it okay when Luo Liang

96
00:06:33,830 --> 00:06:35,159
knows about this video?

97
00:06:35,990 --> 00:06:37,590
I explained it to him before.

98
00:06:40,920 --> 00:06:41,320
Luo...

99
00:06:41,830 --> 00:06:42,630
Who?

100
00:06:43,630 --> 00:06:44,070
I...

101
00:06:44,870 --> 00:06:46,360
I got married a while ago.

102
00:06:49,260 --> 00:06:49,990
Really?

103
00:06:50,500 --> 00:06:52,630
Congratulations, congratulations.

104
00:06:52,680 --> 00:06:53,360
Well, yeah.

105
00:06:53,360 --> 00:06:53,720
Look,

106
00:06:53,720 --> 00:06:55,450
especially at times like this,

107
00:06:55,720 --> 00:06:57,360
your husband should stand behind you

108
00:06:57,360 --> 00:06:59,390
as a solid support,

109
00:06:59,830 --> 00:07:00,120
right?

110
00:07:00,120 --> 00:07:01,870
That's what you call truly reliable.

111
00:07:01,870 --> 00:07:03,720
I'm telling you,
I've seen a lot at the station.

112
00:07:03,720 --> 00:07:05,630
Many couples fight like cats and dogs

113
00:07:05,630 --> 00:07:06,890
over trivial matters.

114
00:07:07,240 --> 00:07:09,040
If your husband has any questions,

115
00:07:09,040 --> 00:07:10,690
tell him to call me.

116
00:07:10,920 --> 00:07:12,900
I'll explain everything clearly to him.

117
00:07:12,900 --> 00:07:14,360
But I have to go on a business trip
these two days.

118
00:07:14,360 --> 00:07:15,130
But it's fine.

119
00:07:15,130 --> 00:07:16,160
I'll have my cybersecurity colleagues

120
00:07:16,160 --> 00:07:17,750
follow up on it.

121
00:07:18,750 --> 00:07:19,190
He...

122
00:07:20,160 --> 00:07:20,950
He won't.

123
00:07:21,070 --> 00:07:21,870
Right, well,

124
00:07:21,870 --> 00:07:23,270
Dr. Luo Liang

125
00:07:23,270 --> 00:07:25,240
is a psychiatrist at Renxin Hospital.

126
00:07:25,240 --> 00:07:26,830
He specializes in helping people

127
00:07:26,830 --> 00:07:27,800
with psychological counseling.

128
00:07:27,800 --> 00:07:29,630
He definitely won't, right?

129
00:07:29,630 --> 00:07:30,430
He won't.

130
00:07:32,120 --> 00:07:38,310
[Sanjie Police Station, Qingzhou Branch,
Lihai Public Security Bureau]

131
00:07:33,950 --> 00:07:34,480
If I had known

132
00:07:34,480 --> 00:07:36,510
those jerks would post this video online,

133
00:07:36,510 --> 00:07:38,870
I definitely wouldn't have dragged you
into this mess.

134
00:07:38,870 --> 00:07:40,159
It was my own choice.

135
00:07:40,159 --> 00:07:41,760
It has nothing to do with you.

136
00:07:42,560 --> 00:07:43,750
I've implicated you.

137
00:07:43,750 --> 00:07:45,260
Don't say that.

138
00:07:45,360 --> 00:07:46,240
I'm a guy.

139
00:07:46,240 --> 00:07:48,080
What does it matter what they say?

140
00:07:48,080 --> 00:07:49,040
You're the one being hurt.

141
00:07:49,040 --> 00:07:50,830
You still have to go back
to the university to teach them.

142
00:07:50,830 --> 00:07:51,290
Well...

143
00:07:52,920 --> 00:07:54,040
But I think,

144
00:07:54,040 --> 00:07:54,950
since Officer Li said

145
00:07:54,950 --> 00:07:55,920
that the video has been deleted,

146
00:07:55,920 --> 00:07:57,310
maybe not many people

147
00:07:57,310 --> 00:07:58,190
have seen it.

148
00:07:59,120 --> 00:08:01,610
So don't overthink it.

149
00:08:02,070 --> 00:08:02,800
And then

150
00:08:03,160 --> 00:08:03,650
go back

151
00:08:03,870 --> 00:08:05,750
and explain it clearly to Luo Liang.

152
00:08:05,750 --> 00:08:06,810
So you two won't...

153
00:08:08,560 --> 00:08:10,360
Anyway, Jiale will stay
at my place for now.

154
00:08:10,360 --> 00:08:11,090
Don't worry.

155
00:08:13,630 --> 00:08:15,690
I have a meeting, so I'll leave first.

156
00:08:16,440 --> 00:08:17,700
D-Don't overthink it.

157
00:08:18,220 --> 00:08:18,680
Bye-bye.

158
00:08:18,290 --> 00:08:23,430
[Sanjie Police Station, Qingzhou Branch,
Lihai Public Security Bureau]

159
00:08:27,950 --> 00:08:28,490
Lu,

160
00:08:28,630 --> 00:08:30,230
take a look at the data for me.

161
00:08:36,630 --> 00:08:37,360
Lu,

162
00:08:37,870 --> 00:08:39,419
we are middle-aged.

163
00:08:39,520 --> 00:08:41,549
You should take it easy on your kidneys.

164
00:08:41,549 --> 00:08:42,830
You play wild now,

165
00:08:43,549 --> 00:08:45,080
but your body can't take it.

166
00:08:48,130 --> 00:08:48,850
Get lost.

167
00:08:49,510 --> 00:08:50,510
I mean well.

168
00:08:52,130 --> 00:08:53,390
Share with me. Tell me.

169
00:08:54,240 --> 00:08:55,230
What are you doing? We're colleagues!

170
00:08:55,230 --> 00:08:56,070
Lu Yifeng!

171
00:08:58,550 --> 00:08:59,810
You've got some nerve.

172
00:09:00,750 --> 00:09:01,550
Is it funny?

173
00:09:05,910 --> 00:09:07,120
A joke is only funny

174
00:09:07,120 --> 00:09:09,610
if the person involved finds it funny.

175
00:09:09,790 --> 00:09:10,870
I'm telling you,

176
00:09:11,020 --> 00:09:12,630
if Lu wasn't such a nice guy,

177
00:09:12,630 --> 00:09:14,600
he could sue you for sexual harassment!

178
00:09:14,600 --> 00:09:15,270
D-D-Don't.

179
00:09:15,270 --> 00:09:16,120
We're colleagues.

180
00:09:16,120 --> 00:09:17,520
There's no need for this.

181
00:09:17,790 --> 00:09:18,360
Well...

182
00:09:18,870 --> 00:09:20,200
What are you looking at?

183
00:09:20,510 --> 00:09:22,080
Apologize to him right now, Mr. Li.

184
00:09:22,080 --> 00:09:22,780
Well...

185
00:09:23,320 --> 00:09:24,150
Lu,

186
00:09:24,600 --> 00:09:25,580
I'm sorry.

187
00:09:28,100 --> 00:09:30,190
Does this mean you've forgiven me?

188
00:09:33,120 --> 00:09:34,120
What do you think?

189
00:09:34,200 --> 00:09:34,720
Yes.

190
00:09:36,000 --> 00:09:36,540
No.

191
00:09:37,030 --> 00:09:38,240
So, is it a yes or a no?

192
00:09:40,270 --> 00:09:41,960
Do you think I came all the way
to your Meteorological Bureau

193
00:09:41,960 --> 00:09:42,910
to have a big fight with someone

194
00:09:42,910 --> 00:09:44,150
just for fun?

195
00:09:45,150 --> 00:09:46,270
I'm still hungry.

196
00:09:46,320 --> 00:09:47,920
Then I'll take you out to eat.

197
00:09:49,510 --> 00:09:51,790
I know it's not about food.

198
00:09:54,080 --> 00:09:54,870
I know.

199
00:09:56,000 --> 00:09:57,000
It's just that...

200
00:09:58,230 --> 00:10:00,090
No matter what reasons I have now,

201
00:10:00,510 --> 00:10:01,270
no matter how I explain it,

202
00:10:01,270 --> 00:10:02,420
I'm in the wrong.

203
00:10:02,790 --> 00:10:04,670
Because I really acted like a jerk.

204
00:10:04,670 --> 00:10:05,270
I'm sorry.

205
00:10:07,880 --> 00:10:10,360
And I'm not good with words,

206
00:10:10,390 --> 00:10:12,200
and I don't know how to sweet-talk.

207
00:10:12,200 --> 00:10:14,730
Because my sweet words
aren't as sweet as you.

208
00:10:15,120 --> 00:10:16,690
Well, do whatever you want.

209
00:10:17,270 --> 00:10:18,670
Just don't ignore me.

210
00:10:19,870 --> 00:10:20,930
Do whatever I want?

211
00:10:25,580 --> 00:10:28,440
Then you can make it up to me
for the rest of your life.

212
00:10:30,870 --> 00:10:31,960
It's a deal then.

213
00:10:33,480 --> 00:10:35,490
Are you crazy?

214
00:10:36,390 --> 00:10:37,720
I promise. I promise.

215
00:10:37,720 --> 00:10:39,770
I promise to treat you very well.

216
00:10:39,870 --> 00:10:40,640
And...

217
00:10:40,670 --> 00:10:41,730
Alright, alright.

218
00:10:43,870 --> 00:10:45,270
Tomorrow is the weekend.

219
00:10:47,120 --> 00:10:48,960
My parents want to meet you.

220
00:10:52,510 --> 00:10:53,630
So sudden?

221
00:10:54,630 --> 00:10:56,650
I'm not ready yet.

222
00:10:57,000 --> 00:10:58,730
What do our parents like to eat?

223
00:10:58,910 --> 00:11:01,200
Don't worry about
what our parents like to eat now.

224
00:11:01,200 --> 00:11:03,200
I'm starving right now.

225
00:11:03,200 --> 00:11:04,120
Spicy skewer hot pot.

226
00:11:04,120 --> 00:11:04,840
With chicken feet.

227
00:11:04,840 --> 00:11:05,150
Okay.

228
00:11:05,150 --> 00:11:05,810
Two of them.

229
00:11:05,870 --> 00:11:06,390
Two jin.

230
00:11:11,200 --> 00:11:12,670
Your mother's name is He Xiao,

231
00:11:12,670 --> 00:11:13,470
from Diannan.

232
00:11:13,670 --> 00:11:15,800
You lived in Chengyu back then, right?

233
00:11:16,440 --> 00:11:18,540
I contacted your father before,

234
00:11:18,720 --> 00:11:19,880
but he seemed

235
00:11:20,000 --> 00:11:22,160
unwilling to talk about the past.

236
00:11:22,480 --> 00:11:24,200
And he said he was rarely home back then,

237
00:11:24,200 --> 00:11:26,120
so he wasn't very clear on the details.

238
00:11:26,120 --> 00:11:28,320
That's why he gave me your contact info.

239
00:11:28,360 --> 00:11:28,910
Yes.

240
00:11:29,320 --> 00:11:31,120
He was always busy making money,

241
00:11:31,440 --> 00:11:32,900
always on business trips.

242
00:11:33,840 --> 00:11:35,330
So, did you spend

243
00:11:35,360 --> 00:11:38,200
more time with your mother growing up?

244
00:11:39,150 --> 00:11:40,550
You must have had a deep bond,

245
00:11:40,550 --> 00:11:41,010
right?

246
00:11:42,460 --> 00:11:43,550
I was young then.

247
00:11:43,870 --> 00:11:44,870
I don't remember.

248
00:11:45,750 --> 00:11:46,970
But your father said

249
00:11:47,390 --> 00:11:49,470
when your mother divorced him,

250
00:11:49,550 --> 00:11:51,480
she didn't fight for your custody.

251
00:11:51,550 --> 00:11:53,150
-Was it because—
-I told you.

252
00:11:53,360 --> 00:11:54,530
I don't remember.

253
00:12:00,080 --> 00:12:00,660
Ma'am.

254
00:12:01,120 --> 00:12:02,870
-Check out our pool and gym.
-No need.

255
00:12:02,870 --> 00:12:03,840
There's a discount for joining now.

256
00:12:03,840 --> 00:12:05,570
-No, thanks.
-No need. No need.

257
00:12:23,750 --> 00:12:25,210
Since you hate her so much,

258
00:12:26,320 --> 00:12:28,550
do you think she cheated

259
00:12:28,550 --> 00:12:30,880
and abandoned the family, including you?

260
00:12:30,910 --> 00:12:31,840
Stop talking!

261
00:12:34,030 --> 00:12:35,230
I forgot everything.

262
00:12:36,550 --> 00:12:37,550
What if I told you

263
00:12:37,550 --> 00:12:39,690
your mother left you and your father,

264
00:12:40,480 --> 00:12:42,080
and even committed suicide,

265
00:12:43,670 --> 00:12:45,730
because she was deceived by a bad man?

266
00:12:52,380 --> 00:12:53,690
I gave up my family.

267
00:12:54,300 --> 00:12:55,660
I gave up my child, too.

268
00:12:56,480 --> 00:12:59,120
I have nothing but him.

269
00:12:59,140 --> 00:13:02,140
Who was the man
who tricked your mother into cheating?

270
00:13:03,000 --> 00:13:04,400
He was a college student,

271
00:13:05,320 --> 00:13:06,380
also from Diannan.

272
00:13:07,150 --> 00:13:09,420
My mom hired him as my tutor then.

273
00:13:10,630 --> 00:13:11,670
That tutor?

274
00:13:12,960 --> 00:13:13,890
What's his name?

275
00:13:19,080 --> 00:13:19,540
Master.

276
00:13:20,150 --> 00:13:20,610
Master.

277
00:13:21,390 --> 00:13:22,510
I still need to confirm something.

278
00:13:22,510 --> 00:13:22,990
Um,

279
00:13:23,550 --> 00:13:24,720
give me one more day off.

280
00:13:24,720 --> 00:13:25,920
Just one day, please?

281
00:13:26,440 --> 00:13:26,960
Hello?

282
00:13:28,010 --> 00:13:28,870
Hello, Master?

283
00:13:29,120 --> 00:13:29,920
The signal...

284
00:13:30,240 --> 00:13:31,240
The signal is bad.

285
00:13:31,550 --> 00:13:33,120
I can't hear you clearly, Master.

286
00:13:33,120 --> 00:13:34,980
