Xiao Yuan,

569
00:26:42,830 --> 00:26:44,350
watch your brother!

570
00:26:47,350 --> 00:26:49,010
Later, we returned to Wuzhou.

571
00:26:50,290 --> 00:26:52,890
They were assigned
to a neighborhood factory.

572
00:26:53,270 --> 00:26:55,110
My dad's temper grew worse.

573
00:26:55,130 --> 00:26:56,180
You shameless wretch!

574
00:26:56,180 --> 00:26:57,310
Such a disgrace!

575
00:26:57,310 --> 00:26:58,360
I'll beat you to death!

576
00:26:58,360 --> 00:27:00,440
-Don't stop me, or I'll beat you too!
-Stop!

577
00:27:00,440 --> 00:27:01,590
The three of us

578
00:27:02,000 --> 00:27:03,310
became his punching bags.

579
00:27:03,310 --> 00:27:05,000
Hung out with those punks, huh?

580
00:27:05,000 --> 00:27:06,260
I'll beat you to death!

581
00:27:06,600 --> 00:27:08,330
You're not afraid of pain, huh?

582
00:27:11,000 --> 00:27:11,600
Come here!

583
00:27:14,000 --> 00:27:15,060
-Come back!
-Yuan!

584
00:27:15,270 --> 00:27:15,890
Yuan!

585
00:27:17,490 --> 00:27:19,490
The only bright spot in my childhood

586
00:27:19,720 --> 00:27:20,590
was my sister.

587
00:27:24,080 --> 00:27:25,480
She took beatings for me,

588
00:27:26,920 --> 00:27:28,280
taught me how to sing,

589
00:27:29,090 --> 00:27:30,240
and cut my hair.

590
00:27:33,480 --> 00:27:35,080
She was known for her beauty.

591
00:27:36,240 --> 00:27:37,580
As long as she was there,

592
00:27:39,270 --> 00:27:40,640
no one dared to bully me.

593
00:27:42,790 --> 00:27:43,990
We had a special bond.

594
00:27:47,470 --> 00:27:49,170
We shared the same birthday,

595
00:27:51,330 --> 00:27:53,190
but she's exactly 12 years older.

596
00:28:00,480 --> 00:28:01,110
Yuan.

597
00:28:02,720 --> 00:28:03,310
Yuan.

598
00:28:20,160 --> 00:28:20,660
Here,

599
00:28:20,960 --> 00:28:21,890
pour some for me.

600
00:28:34,070 --> 00:28:34,880
Does it hurt?

601
00:28:36,440 --> 00:28:36,920
No.

602
00:28:38,640 --> 00:28:39,640
My little doctor.

603
00:28:50,310 --> 00:28:50,750
Look,

604
00:28:52,160 --> 00:28:52,890
an airplane.

605
00:28:57,880 --> 00:28:58,680
Study hard.

606
00:28:59,870 --> 00:29:00,870
When I make money,

607
00:29:00,970 --> 00:29:01,920
I'll take you on an airplane,

608
00:29:01,920 --> 00:29:03,650
and we'll live somewhere else.

609
00:29:17,110 --> 00:29:18,040
Unfortunately,

610
00:29:19,920 --> 00:29:21,250
she was tricked by a man.

611
00:29:24,270 --> 00:29:25,340
♪ My love lingers on your face ♪

612
00:29:25,630 --> 00:29:26,770
♪ Flowing freely to every place ♪

613
00:29:27,170 --> 00:29:29,860
♪ The sun rises above the horizon,
shining bright ♪

614
00:29:36,680 --> 00:29:38,110
Jian!

615
00:29:38,190 --> 00:29:39,390
-Jian!
-Jian!

616
00:29:39,550 --> 00:29:40,510
-Jian!
-Jian!

617
00:29:40,640 --> 00:29:41,500
-Jian!
-Jian!

618
00:29:41,640 --> 00:29:42,440
-Jian!
-Jian!

619
00:29:58,100 --> 00:30:00,570
♪ It's like a dream ♪

620
00:30:01,420 --> 00:30:04,350
♪ Our encounter was so fleeting ♪

621
00:30:05,600 --> 00:30:07,050
♪ You came like a spring breeze ♪

622
00:30:07,340 --> 00:30:11,970
♪ Softly blowing into my heart ♪

623
00:30:12,900 --> 00:30:19,600
♪ Where has your smile gone? ♪

624
00:30:14,270 --> 00:30:15,350
When I was 10,

625
00:30:17,400 --> 00:30:18,440
her boyfriend

626
00:30:19,650 --> 00:30:22,220
got her imprisoned for harboring drugs.

627
00:30:20,450 --> 00:30:26,360
♪ That familiar smile I remember so well ♪

628
00:30:23,000 --> 00:30:23,830
Freeze! Police!

629
00:30:23,830 --> 00:30:24,460
Freeze!

630
00:30:24,880 --> 00:30:25,410
Get down!

631
00:30:26,720 --> 00:30:27,190
Freeze!

632
00:30:26,790 --> 00:30:31,500
♪ Do you know that I love you, miss you,
resent you, and long for you? ♪

633
00:30:27,350 --> 00:30:28,900
Why did you take my guitar?

634
00:30:31,750 --> 00:30:34,200
♪ My love will never change ♪

635
00:30:35,290 --> 00:30:38,960
♪ Have you ever thought about ♪

636
00:30:35,720 --> 00:30:36,450
What is this?

637
00:30:39,270 --> 00:30:42,080
♪ The vow we once made? ♪

638
00:30:39,330 --> 00:30:40,190
Take them away!

639
00:30:42,770 --> 00:30:46,470
♪ Even if you're drawn to the daffodils ♪

640
00:30:42,890 --> 00:30:45,620
I heard she went south
after she got out of prison.

641
00:30:46,750 --> 00:30:49,470
♪ Blooming by the water ♪

642
00:30:48,480 --> 00:30:50,610
She's never returned home since then.

643
00:30:59,930 --> 00:31:00,990
You and your sister

644
00:31:02,510 --> 00:31:04,310
both wanted to escape the family

645
00:31:05,090 --> 00:31:06,380
and your father.

646
00:31:08,000 --> 00:31:09,400
So you changed your name

647
00:31:10,590 --> 00:31:12,520
to make a clean break with the past.

648
00:31:22,000 --> 00:31:23,060
It's not just that.

649
00:31:28,840 --> 00:31:30,380
After my sister left home,

650
00:31:32,470 --> 00:31:33,790
my dad took all his resentment

651
00:31:33,790 --> 00:31:35,000
out on me.

652
00:31:36,060 --> 00:31:37,290
I was often beaten.

653
00:31:39,820 --> 00:31:40,950
I hated this family.

654
00:31:43,510 --> 00:31:45,150
So I studied very hard

655
00:31:46,400 --> 00:31:47,830
to escape that place.

656
00:31:50,960 --> 00:31:52,000
Later, I was admitted to

657
00:31:52,000 --> 00:31:54,260
Dongguang Nanshan Medical University.

658
00:31:56,510 --> 00:31:59,370
I really hoped to become
a good doctor in the future.

659
00:32:00,640 --> 00:32:02,050
It was also at that time

660
00:32:03,920 --> 00:32:05,070
that I met a girl.

661
00:32:11,270 --> 00:32:12,530
Her name is Xu Jingyun.

662
00:32:15,340 --> 00:32:15,720
Paw Patrol,

663
00:32:15,720 --> 00:32:16,830
you've found out so quickly.

664
00:32:16,830 --> 00:32:17,870
You're amazing.

665
00:32:18,270 --> 00:32:20,920
You were the one who noticed
something wrong with his identity.

666
00:32:20,920 --> 00:32:23,200
With the help
of the provincial department,

667
00:32:23,200 --> 00:32:25,200
we found out his real name is Xiao Su.

668
00:32:25,270 --> 00:32:26,750
At Dongguang Nanshan Medical University,

669
00:32:26,750 --> 00:32:29,000
he had a criminal record
during his freshman year.

670
00:32:29,000 --> 00:32:30,460
The victim was Xu Jingyun.

671
00:32:30,590 --> 00:32:31,520
Attempted rape.

672
00:32:32,520 --> 00:32:33,490
Rape?

673
00:32:53,550 --> 00:32:55,720
Are you Ms. Xu Jingyun?

674
00:33:06,750 --> 00:33:07,750
At that time,

675
00:33:08,270 --> 00:33:10,030
did he go against your will?

676
00:33:22,590 --> 00:33:23,550
What did Dad say?

677
00:33:26,310 --> 00:33:27,970
Then you should listen to him.

678
00:33:29,510 --> 00:33:30,920
Have Gao come back later

679
00:33:30,960 --> 00:33:31,750
to pick up

680
00:33:31,750 --> 00:33:32,720
your clothes for changing and stuff.

681
00:33:32,720 --> 00:33:33,980
I'll pack them for you.

682
00:33:40,490 --> 00:33:41,420
It's my husband.

683
00:33:42,720 --> 00:33:45,480
He has a meeting at my father's place
early tomorrow morning,

684
00:33:45,480 --> 00:33:46,940
so he won't be coming back.

685
00:33:56,720 --> 00:33:58,250
Actually, most of the time,

686
00:33:58,960 --> 00:34:00,510
I don't even know

687
00:34:00,530 --> 00:34:01,860
what I really want.

688
00:34:02,560 --> 00:34:04,510
I did like him once.

689
00:34:04,920 --> 00:34:05,920
But I also knew

690
00:34:06,680 --> 00:34:07,920
my father would not agree

691
00:34:07,920 --> 00:34:09,780
to me being with someone like him.

692
00:34:10,110 --> 00:34:11,070
Not to mention,

693
00:34:12,590 --> 00:34:14,440
in that kind of way.

694
00:34:28,150 --> 00:34:29,409
Don't worry, Jingyun.

695
00:34:30,560 --> 00:34:32,110
I won't let him off.

696
00:34:34,590 --> 00:34:35,440
So,

697
00:34:35,800 --> 00:34:37,989
until the very end, you never admitted

698
00:34:38,150 --> 00:34:40,550
that you and Xiao Su
were in a relationship?

699
00:34:41,480 --> 00:34:42,070
No.

700
00:34:53,469 --> 00:34:56,090
I was sentenced to 3 years
for attempted rape.

701
00:34:58,800 --> 00:35:00,200
After I got out of prison,

702
00:35:01,230 --> 00:35:03,030
I couldn't continue my studies.

703
00:35:06,660 --> 00:35:07,390
And my hand

704
00:35:08,910 --> 00:35:11,440
made it impossible
for me to become a surgeon.

705
00:35:13,160 --> 00:35:14,890
But she never explained a word.

706
00:35:17,890 --> 00:35:19,430
She never even saw me again.

707
00:35:21,430 --> 00:35:23,490
My father was very angry at that time.

708
00:35:25,070 --> 00:35:27,730
He immediately arranged for me
to study abroad.

709
00:35:31,440 --> 00:35:32,440
Only one thing...

710
00:35:34,150 --> 00:35:34,710
What?

711
00:35:39,800 --> 00:35:41,030
Attempted rape

712
00:35:43,030 --> 00:35:44,490
carries a lighter penalty

713
00:35:46,110 --> 00:35:47,310
than completed rape.

714
00:35:48,960 --> 00:35:49,920
By saying that,

715
00:35:51,150 --> 00:35:53,150
I saved my father from humiliation.

716
00:35:54,800 --> 00:35:56,600
It was also the only small effort

717
00:35:57,150 --> 00:35:59,280
I could make for Xiao Su.

718
00:36:01,470 --> 00:36:02,800
For the first few years,

719
00:36:04,440 --> 00:36:05,370
I was very angry.

720
00:36:07,840 --> 00:36:09,570
I hated her for turning our love

721
00:36:10,840 --> 00:36:12,480
into a crime that was humiliated

722
00:36:12,480 --> 00:36:13,680
and mocked by others.

723
00:36:16,540 --> 00:36:18,390
I hated her for ruining my life.

724
00:36:21,710 --> 00:36:22,740
But later on,

725
00:36:24,000 --> 00:36:25,270
I gradually let it go.

726
00:36:28,410 --> 00:36:30,230
Maybe she just chose to protect herself

727
00:36:30,230 --> 00:36:31,550
in that moment.

728
00:36:38,230 --> 00:36:39,230
She's not like me.

729
00:36:40,150 --> 00:36:41,320
I have no one to depend on,

730
00:36:41,320 --> 00:36:42,720
and no one cares about me.

731
00:36:45,230 --> 00:36:46,890
I believe she had her reasons.

732
00:36:49,190 --> 00:36:50,070
Since then,

733
00:36:52,760 --> 00:36:54,560
my life has completely changed.

734
00:36:56,400 --> 00:36:58,000
I didn't dare to tell anyone,

735
00:36:59,440 --> 00:37:01,700
and I just sneaked back to Diannan alone.

736
00:37:02,510 --> 00:37:04,440
But I didn't want to accept my fate.

737
00:37:05,910 --> 00:37:09,170
I didn't want to live like my parents
for the rest of my life.

738
00:37:09,420 --> 00:37:11,340
Until I met a fresh graduate.

739
00:37:12,940 --> 00:37:14,140
His name is Luo Liang.

740
00:37:16,280 --> 00:37:17,190
He's an orphan.

741
00:37:19,670 --> 00:37:20,480
His grades were bad,

742
00:37:20,480 --> 00:37:23,410
and he didn't want
to take the college entrance exam.

743
00:37:23,510 --> 00:37:24,840
I discussed it with him,

744
00:37:25,710 --> 00:37:26,910
bought his identity,

745
00:37:28,530 --> 00:37:30,030
took the exam again,

746
00:37:30,920 --> 00:37:32,180
and started a new life.

747
00:37:34,110 --> 00:37:34,960
Until today.

748
00:37:37,990 --> 00:37:38,850
Just like that,

749
00:37:40,230 --> 00:37:41,440
I went from Xiao Su

750
00:37:41,440 --> 00:37:42,550
to Luo Liang.

751
00:37:48,850 --> 00:37:49,710
Just like that?

752
00:37:54,710 --> 00:37:56,710
Then why didn't you tell me earlier?

753
00:38:01,510 --> 00:38:02,640
Maybe just like you,

754
00:38:05,510 --> 00:38:06,890
I didn't want to face

755
00:38:07,000 --> 00:38:08,530
such an embarrassing past.

756
00:38:10,990 --> 00:38:12,650
But I told you everything.

757
00:38:14,070 --> 00:38:15,360
I hid nothing from you.

758
00:38:24,630 --> 00:38:25,760
That time Jiale called me

759
00:38:25,760 --> 00:38:27,020
and said you were sick,

760
00:38:28,870 --> 00:38:30,330
you told me in the hospital

761
00:38:31,920 --> 00:38:33,720
that you got your father killed.

762
00:38:35,000 --> 00:38:36,460
I thought your inner demon

763
00:38:37,030 --> 00:38:38,890
was the guilt towards your father

764
00:38:39,920 --> 00:38:42,650
and the terrible relationship
with your mother.

765
00:38:43,920 --> 00:38:45,230
But it's not, right?

766
00:38:47,920 --> 00:38:49,250
You were in so much pain,

767
00:38:49,710 --> 00:38:50,710
so broken down.

768
00:38:53,280 --> 00:38:55,800
Was it because Ding Zhibo
announced the scholarship

769
00:38:55,800 --> 00:38:57,680
established for you on that day?

770
00:39:03,920 --> 00:39:06,420
But I told you about Ding Zhibo.

771
00:39:07,710 --> 00:39:08,710
You knew it.

772
00:39:10,360 --> 00:39:13,000
If he hadn't insisted on
taking that little girl away

773
00:39:13,000 --> 00:39:14,360
in front of you,

774
00:39:16,220 --> 00:39:17,820
would you still have said it?

775
00:39:26,410 --> 00:39:27,210
I understand.

776
00:39:30,840 --> 00:39:33,840
I can understand
your reservations and concealment.

777
00:39:35,320 --> 00:39:36,550
Because we are both

778
00:39:36,550 --> 00:39:38,440
fighting the pain of the past,

779
00:39:40,030 --> 00:39:41,560
not wanting to be defeated,

780
00:39:43,110 --> 00:39:43,920
while also

781
00:39:43,920 --> 00:39:44,880
desperately

782
00:39:45,590 --> 00:39:47,550
trying to hide this ugly wound.

783
00:39:50,430 --> 00:39:52,160
But we are all very conflicted,

784
00:39:53,480 --> 00:39:54,540
wanting to hide it,

785
00:39:56,320 --> 00:39:58,250
but also hoping that at some point,

786
00:39:59,480 --> 00:40:01,320
this wound could be seen

787
00:40:03,880 --> 00:40:04,800
and comforted.

788
00:40:11,070 --> 00:40:13,070
I know now is not the best time,

789
00:40:16,440 --> 00:40:17,370
but at least I show you

790
00:40:17,370 --> 00:40:18,250
mine.

791
00:40:23,320 --> 00:40:24,120
You know what?

792
00:40:26,400 --> 00:40:27,260
When you told me

793
00:40:29,400 --> 00:40:30,800
and confessed your past,

794
00:40:32,230 --> 00:40:32,710
saying

795
00:40:33,920 --> 00:40:34,920
not to leave you,

796
00:40:36,880 --> 00:40:38,190
not to leave you alone,

797
00:40:40,710 --> 00:40:41,800
my heart ached.

798
00:40:45,460 --> 00:40:46,460
For so many years,

799
00:40:48,030 --> 00:40:49,710
you must have cried

800
00:40:49,710 --> 00:40:51,240
alone on countless nights.

801
00:40:54,510 --> 00:40:55,650
Because I did too.

802
00:40:59,670 --> 00:41:00,670
I am lucky

803
00:41:02,590 --> 00:41:03,710
to have met you.

804
00:41:06,710 --> 00:41:08,670
It feels like destiny.

805
00:41:11,280 --> 00:41:12,070
The two of us

806
00:41:14,100 --> 00:41:16,630
are the best gifts
from heaven for each other.

807
00:41:20,210 --> 00:41:22,070
As someone who has also been hurt,

808
00:41:22,800 --> 00:41:25,400
I can better understand
the pain in your heart.

809
00:41:28,230 --> 00:41:29,360
But I also know

810
00:41:31,070 --> 00:41:32,600
we are different after all.

811
00:41:33,990 --> 00:41:35,610
I can accept all of you.

812
00:41:37,410 --> 00:41:38,560
But I don't expect

813
00:41:39,280 --> 00:41:41,080
you to make the same choice as me.

814
00:42:35,600 --> 00:42:37,370
[Marriage Certificate]

815
00:42:40,150 --> 00:42:42,040
[Marriage Certificate]

816
00:42:40,210 --> 00:42:42,010
If you choose to leave in the end,

817
00:42:44,840 --> 00:42:46,370
I can completely accept it.

818
00:42:49,230 --> 00:42:50,830
You can write the agreement.

819
00:42:51,880 --> 00:42:52,820
This house

820
00:42:53,280 --> 00:42:54,880
will be left to you and Jiale.

821
00:42:58,000 --> 00:42:59,500
Is that all you have to say?

822
00:43:04,070 --> 00:43:06,200
The time we had dinner with you and Mom,

823
00:43:09,940 --> 00:43:12,670
the woman next to me
wasn't my biological mother.

824
00:43:15,880 --> 00:43:18,540
I was really afraid
to let you see this side of me.

825
00:43:20,030 --> 00:43:21,670
So I found someone to help.

826
00:43:25,710 --> 00:43:27,440
I know I was ridiculous.

827
00:43:29,190 --> 00:43:29,920
I'm sorry.

828
00:43:44,460 --> 00:43:48,790
[The Dark Romance]

829
00:43:52,480 --> 00:43:54,700
[2000]
[Dongguang Nanshan Medical University]

830
00:44:01,000 --> 00:44:01,510
It's raining so heavily.

831
00:44:01,510 --> 00:44:02,440
Why are you here?

832
00:44:03,630 --> 00:44:05,760
How will you go back in such heavy rain?

833
00:44:06,920 --> 00:44:07,850
Then wait for me.

834
00:44:08,110 --> 00:44:09,110
I'll be done soon.

835
00:44:14,110 --> 00:44:15,120
Your hair

836
00:44:15,280 --> 00:44:16,540
is blocking your eyes.

837
00:44:18,850 --> 00:44:19,450
Stop it.

838
00:44:24,480 --> 00:44:26,190
Usually,
if someone asks me to cut their hair,

839
00:44:26,190 --> 00:44:27,450
I wouldn't be willing.

840
00:44:54,440 --> 00:44:55,270
Not here.

841
00:44:55,670 --> 00:44:57,600
We are doomed if someone finds out.

842
00:45:00,630 --> 00:45:01,440
It's so late.

843
00:45:04,320 --> 00:45:05,520
No one will come.

844
00:45:08,530 --> 00:45:09,590
What are you doing?

845
00:45:12,000 --> 00:45:12,800
Don't touch me!
